  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate if the use of perioperative neuraxial blockade reduces post-operative
      mortality and cardiorespiratory events compared to intraoperative general anesthesia AND
      postoperative IV narcotic analgesia. This is a feasibility study to determine if recruitment
      and execution of the protocol could be done in a timely manner in a much larger trial
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
